{"title":"对死亡贩子的警告","authors":["马凡陀"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":10,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"对死亡贩子的警告"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举起我们的旗子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把它举得高高！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这全世界共同的旗子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这全世界七十二国人民共"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同的愿望："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“保卫民主！保卫和平！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举起我们的旗子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把它举得高高！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在伟大的苏联，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在光荣的中华人民共和国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在东欧人民民主国家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在希腊、越南、印尼……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在五大洲凡是有人类居住"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的地方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的旗子高举，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的旗子飘扬！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华尔街的大资本家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了他们的钱包，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了挽救他们的灭亡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阴谋发动新的战争，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要叫全世界人民流血，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要叫全世界的城市、田庄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"变成战场！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是我们坚决的回答："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民不分国界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民不分肤色，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民要的是和平建设："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学校、剧场、画廊、托儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民要生活得更好、更美，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民不要破坏和死亡！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民反对你战争的挑拨者，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民反对你穿大礼服戴白"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手套，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满口“西方文明”的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杀戮婴孩、制造孤儿寡妇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金元魔王！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英勇的中国人民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用刀，用斧，用梭标，用"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地雷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用美国制造的火箭炮，冲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锋枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打断了这魔王的腿！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打败了他的走狗—"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"—蒋介石！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们爱我们的国家、我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的自由，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们知道用什么方法"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来回答侵略者！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在巴黎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在布拉格，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在纽约——这帝国主义的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心脏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在莫斯科，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在布达佩斯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在墨西哥城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在新中国的北京，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民组织了强大的示威，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举起千千万万个拳头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举向你死亡的贩子！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你用不发护照来阻挡吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“真理是不需要护照才走"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路的！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你用唱对台戏来企图遮掩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，那是多么可笑的一批"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"色情作家、托匪、流氓呀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民连唾沫也不屑吐向这"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"些拿着笔杆的豺狼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处是人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处是民主、和平的爱好"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"者，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处是文化、自由的保卫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"者，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处是我们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处是守候着你们的步枪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和手榴弹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处的人民准备着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处是你们的死路！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战争贩子们！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是全世界人民的坚决的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回答："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们在什么地方发动战争，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么地方就是你们的坟墓！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}